{"tid":602531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[我唔係屈機男]可恥,借斷腳媽上位","createTime":"2018-03-23T05:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T13:56:31.000Z","uid":99805,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b4db1dbaa4ca7a52eb2ab55408c04603a3060463","tid":602531,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"我唔係屈機男 #40470卑鄙過一日<br />\n<br />\n話說早兩日有個post&quot;有無屋企有D家底既人諗住唔番工做二世祖&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/600110/page/5\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/600110/page/5</a><br />\n人地好地地傾緊,呢條咁既保安仔衝出去叫人捐錢比寶馬車禍既斷腳媽<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/131344_cb0b966a605797d9b9dcbac5096495a8.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F131344_cb0b966a605797d9b9dcbac5096495a8.PNG&h=410d6dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中間點撚佢就唔多講啦,簡單講就係又答應捐錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/132004_6c607db21d7f95b27ddbb915316b6faa.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F132004_6c607db21d7f95b27ddbb915316b6faa.PNG&h=21eae113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">平時開post回post唔係扮人生導師就鬧人死乞兒都算,今次仲借個斷腳媽上位</span><br />\n<br />\n呢條友既藉口都好笑架啦,比人踢爆佢係高登既保安雞蟲屈機男就話自己唔係真正屈機男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/132240_978d46b06a31f1ac546cdd25876855c6.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F132240_978d46b06a31f1ac546cdd25876855c6.PNG&h=5d396b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n次次都拋人敢唔敢捐錢,次次都郁底收尾<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n劇情回顧:<br />\n屈機男在高登常以有錢佬姿態教化高登仔做人道理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0i1Q28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0i1Q28.jpg&h=c884d968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屈機男常自稱有幾個物業, 但又睇淡樓市<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1Bp683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1Bp683.jpg&h=14ab5e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69n6byc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69n6byc.jpg&h=508c64cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屈機男以高高在上姿態雄霸財經台, 而且有一眾信眾追隨.<br />\n然而, 直至會員 米已成炊出現, 他質疑屈機男之有錢言論, 多次挑戰其財經台權威.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3u76373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3u76373.jpg&h=476a844a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是大發明家屈機男發明了解決糾紛方法...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ly869i3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLy869i3.jpg&h=be0daf5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/009PHw5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F009PHw5.jpg&h=dcad78a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屈機男及其信眾一直強勢, 欺侮米已成炊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKrCVnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKrCVnV.jpg&h=33bd4d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgX65WO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgX65WO.jpg&h=c0ddb46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVg6J3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVg6J3M.jpg&h=f50358a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都係直接飛到結局.... 屈機男捐唔起錢認輸, 而其信眾亦鳥獸散或深潛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6d859G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6d859G.jpg&h=bb060f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw1pgUy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw1pgUy.jpg&h=7c7dbc8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8NL1v6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8NL1v6.png&h=401336d2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n引用返巴打講<br />\n<blockquote>做男人柒左唔緊要<br />\n唔好衰左之後咁撚多藉口</blockquote><br />\n高登柒頭回顧 屈機男<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/64383/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/64383/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"21d121701b746b2c49beff62fa8641f16ce2b852","tid":602531,"uid":126029,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:25:02.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4ff0ea998a0092c85dab788ee788f07dc0324b","tid":602531,"uid":99805,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"21d121701b746b2c49beff62fa8641f16ce2b852","tid":602531,"uid":126029,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:25:02.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:31:48.000Z","msg":"個個post都要關你事先開得? 會唔會睇得自己太高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0733039fb5cf0c546802a3d35a8cbf79fb8b71","tid":602531,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"將個波推落蘋果到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/133230_23a009b3a13b82891dfa25f4a89420a6.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F133230_23a009b3a13b82891dfa25f4a89420a6.PNG&h=38ea25bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再次出黎扮專家講樓市<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/602283/page/6\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/602283/page/6</a><br />\n&quot;前幾日千二萬買將軍澳果對夫婦 而家諗緊咩&quot;<br />\n<br />\n咁我一定問佢幾時找數<br />\n好撚野,自己話捐比斷腳媽,唔知貼乜春出黎混淆視線<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/133359_2dc5920c075e8a0c6b8a471e9d8874de.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F133359_2dc5920c075e8a0c6b8a471e9d8874de.PNG&h=af30ebd0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcaead5c528f7a631540c8e5132cb6919e4d6390","tid":602531,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"呀保安仔話2日唔敢入返去個POST係因為要訓教<br />\n先唔覺佢係咪訓足48小時啦,當我一按個起底掣<br />\n呀....呢48小時竟然有出post,開post仲密過佢老母流白帶<br />\n夠膽死話因為訓教所以唔回<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/133813_f7f0bbdb094d0b83d7561fc5ec2130d7.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F133813_f7f0bbdb094d0b83d7561fc5ec2130d7.PNG&h=e4d45ac3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d41a4ef412ad4057bc3c22da74f81feeab7b4b6b","tid":602531,"uid":3109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"條友由舊登乞食乞到黎連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537f13658600e94b017b449d912a8e8320f2b6d6","tid":602531,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"block 左咪算囉<br />\n<br />\n人地返工時間開post , 你控制唔到<br />\n<br />\n你樓下石Q 做足十二個鐘嫁 ... <br />\n<br />\n慳埋慳埋叫下雞上網FF 自己幾有錢已經好慘"},{"pid":"8b085f3b0c0a75c72d6be449a61d5a9216760368","tid":602531,"uid":99805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d41a4ef412ad4057bc3c22da74f81feeab7b4b6b","tid":602531,"uid":3109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"條友由舊登乞食乞到黎連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:47:22.000Z","msg":"條友唔知點解好鍾意上網話人窮鬼乞衣廢柴<br />\n應該係典型上網刷現實無既&quot;富豪感&quot;<br />\n同埋有巴打起過佢底係讀I大,所以成日上網鬧母校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/602158/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/602158/page/2</a><br />\n見到D乞衣平時唔捨得使錢，慳埋慳埋買股票輸鳩晒...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/597752/page/1?post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/597752/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n老實講，IVE仔點睇自己前景？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/592270/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/592270/page/1</a><br />\n廢柴讀唔成書就走去讀ive逃避現實<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/567479/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/567479/page/1</a><br />\n8成連登仔係社會低下層地底泥<br />\n<br />\n搵得55都咁多口水充闊佬(真係55既話)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/564432/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/564432/page/1</a><br />\n香港人搵錢其實唔多<br />\n<br />\n過年都要刷存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/562559/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/562559/page/1</a><br />\n年初一都唔見你班連登仔post恭賀說話，就知你地係低下層"},{"pid":"969309257d9aa4031e73affb3287aa99e4b74bc4","tid":602531,"uid":146243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"又係呢條垃圾 仆街死未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d7ca547b3817387755ce6f85d608bee0b5ed8f","tid":602531,"uid":99805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"現實幾咁窮先可以日日上網扮有錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/134940_61ea8fa0d2f23f68c85f1a5e911fcbc2.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F134940_61ea8fa0d2f23f68c85f1a5e911fcbc2.PNG&h=b203b6ed&s={SIZE